description:
The Dahlia Headband is carefully hand cut & sewn to perfection with my own little hands & heart using 100% wool felt. The piece stays in place with a very comfy hidden black elastic band. So sweet!

{dimensions}
4" (length) x 2" (width) inches approximately.

{adjustments}
All my hair accessories are made to order, allowing me to make custom adjustments for you. Let me know if you'd like an item made for an adult, child or babe, made into a snap clip, bobby pin, french barrette or an elastic band. I'm happy to customize your order, free of charge. Just specify upon checkout, in the note to seller section, exactly how you'd like your item.

{care}
Dry clean only.

{commissions}
I accept commissions & love making them. Just contact me with the details of that special little item in your head & I'll happily discuss options & pricing with you.

{help}
For more information, please visit my website & don't hesitate to contact me if you would like additional clarification.

{please note}
Because I work with Vintage Materials, such as the lace & buttons featured in this collection, these elements may not be the exact ones featured in photos due to quantities on hand. I will always try to find similar materials to those featured in photos. Thanks for understanding & for your support!

